  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Needs Review\n129\nDream Thursday night 6-11-81:\n\nI am with Nancy. She is behaving unusually: she is very active and energetic. I am told that she took something, a medication. She now has an additional mind or psyche in her, that of a man. The names John and Bill are mentioned, and there is some reference to the ending of the BTA novel. I want to take the medication, too, so it will happen to me. The medication is shown me; it is in a cylinder or carton on which writing appears. I can't read the ",
      "matched_alias": "Israel",
      "term_id": "TERM_israel",
      "term_name": "Israel",
      "term_slug": "israel"
    }
  ],
